  "body": "develop ac85fdc\n\nsend a tx with gasprice 0\n\n```\nI0506 20:42:27.825445   30778 api.go:42] eth_sendTransaction [{\"from\":\"0xcd2a3d9f938e13cd947ec05abc7fe734df8dd826\",\"gas\":\"0x2dc6c0\",\"gasPrice\":\"0x0\",\"to\":\"0xb61662398570293e4f0d25525e2b3002b7fe0836\",\"data\":\"\"}]\nI0506 20:42:27.828432   30778 transaction_pool.go:176] (t) 6364326133643966 => b6166239 (0x66a100) 18bd6887b64641a08c09f4be5263443bb31794876421fe09833649d323a4f147\nI0506 20:42:27.828539   30778 xeth.go:723] Tx(18bd6887b64641a08c09f4be5263443bb31794876421fe09833649d323a4f147) to: &b61662398570293e4f0d25525e2b3002b7fe0836\nI0506 20:42:27.828609   30778 http.go:130] Generated response: *rpc.RpcSuccessResponse &{%!s(float64=17) 2.0 0x18bd6887b64641a08c09f4be5263443bb31794876421fe09833649d323a4f147}\nI0506 20:42:27.828684   30778 http.go:141] Sending payload: {\n    \"id\": 17,\n    \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n    \"result\": \"0x18bd6887b64641a08c09f4be5263443bb31794876421fe09833649d323a4f147\"\n}\n```\n\nEXPECTED:  Out of gas should not lose any wei since gasprice is 0.\n\nOBSERVED:  gasprice of 10 szabo was charged.  Lost many wei instead of 0.\n\ncurl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionByHash\",\"params\":[\"0x18bd6887b64641a08c09f4be5263443bb31794876421fe09833649d323a4f147\"],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8080\n\n```\n{\n  \"result\": {\n    \"input\": \"\",\n    \"gasPrice\": \"0x9184e72a000\",\n    \"gas\": \"0x2dc6c0\",\n    \"hash\": \"0x18bd6887b64641a08c09f4be5263443bb31794876421fe09833649d323a4f147\",\n    \"nonce\": \"0x169d\",\n    \"blockHash\": \"0xe32af77bf14fe0fa4d696c765eddbfeb2b9629be2e4131b2993c439a946fb75b\",\n    \"blockNumber\": \"0x4145f\",\n    \"transactionIndex\": \"0x0\",\n    \"from\": \"0xcd2a3d9f938e13cd947ec05abc7fe734df8dd826\",\n    \"to\": \"0xb61662398570293e4f0d25525e2b3002b7fe0836\",\n    \"value\": \"0x0\"\n  },\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\n  \"id\": 1\n}\n```\n",
