    "body": "The transaction you're showing has a gas price set:\n\n```\n    \"gasPrice\": \"0x9184e72a000\",\n    \"gas\": \"0x2dc6c0\",\n```\n\nDid you use the `eth.resend` feature? Resending a transaction which had a zero gas price and resending it without a new gas price will, as a side effect of `big.Int` set the default gas price.\n",
